<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4669359>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 13. Pilargis rozbaczyloi n. sp. (A, B) Holotype SSUC-6901: (A) right setiger 12 in anterior view; (B) same, right setiger 45 in anterior view. (C, D) Paratype SSUC-6902: (C) right setiger 45 in anterior view (insert: glands, enlarged); (D) same, right setiger 90 in anterior view (insert: glands, enlarged). (E, F) Paratype SSUC-6906: (E) right setiger 50 in posterior view; (F) same, neurosetae with tip eroded. Scale bars: 150 mm (A); 112 mm (B); 180 mm (C, E); 225 mm (D); 34 mm (F)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4669359/files/figure.png" .

